    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "<p>At Induscraft, we craft timeless furniture rooted in tradition and designed for modern living. Every piece reflects thoughtful design, skilled craftsmanship, and a deep respect for natural materials.</p>"
